{"tid":1798162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突破盲點］和你shop轉玩法","createTime":"2019-12-26T04:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T07:24:17.000Z","uid":247211,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"48709a6a59702738af7cd658489d232a23fb9091","tid":1798162,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"呢兩日有份和你shop既應該會留意到便衣狗有幾個特點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 大部分黑色面巾（少量口罩）<br />\n2. 有個背囊/斜孭袋<br />\n3. 佢地唔會blackbloc<br />\n4. 挨住D牆或者欄杆監視<br />\n<br />\n係唔捉鬼既前提下，所有和理非更加應該純粹行街裝，口罩背囊都唔使帶，勇武做野既時候見到非blackbloc既面罩背囊友可以更加容易提防，甚至可以上前友善地查問，check到就召喚神獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最理想就梗係勇武B趁住大量狗部署係商場既時候偷雞其他地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981e80a351404ae253663b7a755dfc336b2fdbc0","tid":1798162,"uid":106480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"[警世] 獨立定自治? 中共分化手段之一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1798099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1798099</a><br />\n有興趣來睇下"},{"pid":"b07936ad688ae4de5dc1cb0e6563ff20ae5b94c1","tid":1798162,"uid":247211,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:38:52.000Z","msg":"仲有一點就係：<br />\n<br />\n完成任務落閘就可以走，轉其他商場<br />\n唔好迷戀陣地戰，商場落左閘就算再開返<br />\n你估仲有冇人去買野？入都入唔到啦"},{"pid":"ffaedda8e84b90d26dad1dbfc316d95c3402dab3","tid":1798162,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ba60fbf88b9120d6a6eb4e1e883ff5eca1689a77","tid":1798162,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:54:03.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"08829abfd8f2b2f53300033a0e86239ae27354ae","tid":1798162,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:54:43.000Z","msg":"普通裝就得<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"cdf71f00b73756a97dc31d960cefdef40a68b38e","tid":1798162,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"42dc266b83f846d7d22ae8caf31bcee9a716cf2b","tid":1798162,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"其實全人類一齊搭升降機同扶手梯都可以做到效果,唔一定blackbloc個喎, <br />\n人少少都可以塞到ground floor 同埋冇人會上到上面行"},{"pid":"d1523274bcb6170877180c2fee9a760c0336bfd2","tid":1798162,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"耳機，"},{"pid":"bd4d92eb70fbc6eb2a44c11cf334334c386774f3","tid":1798162,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:24:34.000Z","msg":"銀髮手足可以上前鬧番佢地做曱甴暴徒搞搞震 睇下反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21701b205ccef19bfd521ee5e6d46b57cc926a2f","tid":1798162,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"多狗就拉返出去路面 拉散警力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cad48efd0ed366a7887bf4b33b9aea6e4f7e95a","tid":1798162,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"聖誕約左女神?<br />\n梗係企定定商場等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e21f9348e7f2ab3fb0d11753ae2dfa0bae9be3f","tid":1798162,"uid":278990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"記住目的只係阻消費，別送頭"},{"pid":"520729115ec145379c46bfd8df38d99be1163460","tid":1798162,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"aa7b1e0c5a67be90b52d3181eabd304877431b6f","tid":1798162,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21701b205ccef19bfd521ee5e6d46b57cc926a2f","tid":1798162,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201